assetProfile.longBusinessSummary: Felissimo Corporation sells a range of lifestyle products in Japan. It offers ladies' fashion, including tops, one- pieces, tunics, outerwear, bottoms, formal wear, coordinate sets, pajamas, homewear, and other ladies fashion; bags, wallets, pouches, shoes, insoles, and other shoes goods ; fashion goods, including accessories, watches, hats, belts, leg wear, handkerchiefs, umbrella, rain gears, glasses, sun glasses, stoles, mufflers, gloves, and other fashion items; men's fashion, including men's tops, men's outerwear, men's bottoms, men's pajamas, homewear, men's Inner Garments, and other men's Fashion Items; underwear including, bra, panties, top undergarments, bottom undergarments, and other underwear; and kid's garments, unisex items, kids' sundries, babies' clothing, and babies' sundries. It also offers handicraft kit sets that includes knitting, embroideries, patchworks quilting, crafting, handicraft goods, tools, and other handicraft kit sets; kitchen utensils, including tableware, cooking goods, lunch goods, kitchen aprons, and other kitchen utensils; beauty and health care products, including cosmetic and make-up items; and stationary items, such as stamps, seals, envelopes, lettersets, masking tapes, memo pad, calendar, writing material, wrapping goods, and other stationery. In addition, it offers food items. The company offers its products through catalog and internet. Felissimo Corporation was founded in 1965 and is headquartered in Kobe, Japan.
